	 New Delhi (PTI): An attempt to rob around 3,000 textbooks from NCERT headquarters in Delhi on Monday was foiled by guards deployed on the campus. Some people, who came in three cars and a motorcycle, were loading textbooks in the vehicles when a security guard spotted them, police said.                  
